T02TD3188E:200b-4: sngar bshad pa'i cho gas yi ge mu: ser po yongs su gyur pa las 'jam dpal gzhon nur gyur pa zhal gsum phyag drug pa ste /
T02TD3188E:200b-5: zhal gur gum 'od kyi mdog dang /
T02TD3188E:200b-6: g-yas pa dang cig shos ni snon po dang dkar po /
T02TD3188E:200b-7: sems dpa'i skyil krung gis bzhugs pa /
T02TD3188E:200b-8: g-yas pa'i phyag gsum ni ral gri dang /
T02TD3188E:200b-9: mda' dang mchog sbyin pa dang ldan la /
T02TD3188E:200b-10: g-yon pa'i phyag gsum na ni shes rab kyi pha rol tu phyin pa'i glegs bam dang /
T02TD3188E:200b-13: sgeg pa'i nyams bag dang ldan pa'i gzhon nu'i rgyan dang /
T02TD3188E:200b-14: na bza' la sogs pa can /
T02TD3188E:200b-15: me tog la sogs pas mdzes pa chen por gyur pa'i zur phud gsum gyis rnam par mdzes pa /
T02TD3188E:200b-16: de bzhin gshegs pa'i rdul phra rab las grub par bdag nyid bsgoms la /
T02TD3188E:200b-17: aom mu: zhes bya ba'i sngags 'di bzlas par bya ba'o //
T02TD3188E:200b-19: aa bha ya'i zhal snga nas dge slong tshul khrims rgyal mtshan gyis bsgyur ba'o//
